{"prompt": "Build a user-friendly site for a community garden initiative. The design should prominently display a bright lime green.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Green Thumb Community Garden</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f0fff0; /* Lightest green background */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #32cd32; /* Lime Green */\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid #228b22; /* Forest Green for contrast */\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #2e8b57; /* Sea Green */\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .intro-section, .about-section, .get-involved-section {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .intro-section img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            border: 3px solid #32cd32; /* Lime Green border */\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #32cd32; /* Lime Green */\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #228b22; /* Darker green on hover */\n        }\n        .benefits-list {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n        .benefits-list li {\n            background-color: #e0ffff; /* Light Cyan */\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin: 10px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-align: center;\n            width: 200px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .benefits-list li strong {\n            color: #32cd32; /* Lime Green */\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background-color: #32cd32; /* Lime Green */\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Green Thumb Community Garden</h1>\n        <p>Growing Together, Nourishing Our Community</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"intro-section\">\n            <h2>Welcome to Our Garden!</h2>\n            <p>Join us in cultivating a vibrant green space where neighbors can connect, learn, and grow fresh, healthy food together.</p>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/800x300/90EE90/ffffff?text=Community+Garden+Life\" alt=\"People gardening in a community garden\">\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"about-section\">\n            <h2>About Our Initiative</h2>\n            <p>The Green Thumb Community Garden is a volunteer-led project dedicated to promoting sustainable urban agriculture, fostering community engagement, and providing access to fresh produce for everyone. We believe in the power of shared spaces and the joy of growing your own food.</p>\n            <h3>What We Offer:</h3>\n            <ul class=\"benefits-list\">\n                <li><p><strong>Shared Plots:</strong> Access to communal garden beds.</p></li>\n                <li><p><strong>Workshops:</strong> Learning opportunities on gardening techniques.</p></li>\n                <li><p><strong>Community Events:</strong> Social gatherings and harvest celebrations.</p></li>\n                <li><p><strong>Tool Sharing:</strong> Access to shared gardening equipment.</p></li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"get-involved-section\">\n            <h2>Get Involved</h2>\n            <p>Whether you're a seasoned gardener or a complete beginner, there's a place for you! Help us make our garden bloom.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More & Sign Up</a>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Green Thumb Community Garden. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p id=\"contact\">Contact us at: info@greenthumbgarden.org</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}